message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously designed to meet your specific needs. Given its high value and quality, it's worth no less than $12,000 to us. Considering its worth to you is $8,000, I propose we strike a fair deal. Would you be interested in acquiring this product for $9,500? This price reflects a thoughtful compromise that takes into account both the value we place on the product and your perceived worth to it.
